              ],
              "free_text": [
                "4 passivated implanted planar silicon detectors",
                "with active areas of 0.3 cm2. They were placed at a",
                "distance of 14 cm from the target and at the",
                "laboratory angles of  105,120,135, and 150 degr.",
                "Each detector was shielded by a 2mu-m thick foil of",
                "aluminized Mylar in order to stop the intense flux of",
                "elastically scattered protons. The average solid angle",
                "per detector was found to be (1.42+-0.04)*10**(-2)."
              ]
            }
          ],
